description: A set of e-mail components which implement IMAP, SMTP, POP3 protocols with SSL support, parsing and building MIME and S/MIME messages, Outlook .MSG and .PST conversions, mail merge over database, OAuth 2.0, DNS MX lookup, e-mail address validation, parsing winmail.dat, bounced messages processing, HTML messages cleanup, messages with embedded pictures, and much more.
releaseNotes: AES encryption for S/MIME, MIME parser optimizations and UTF-32 support, improved winmail.dat parser, Folder.Archive flag support in IMAP module.
